  Odylith -->|Open proof| Atlas
  Odylith -->|Open proof| Compass

  Radar -->|Native evidence only| Odylith
  Registry -->|Native evidence only| Odylith
  Casebook -->|Native evidence only| Odylith
  Atlas -->|Native evidence only| Odylith
  Compass -->|Native evidence only| Odylith
